---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import BlockChain from '../../../public/assets/blockchain.svg';
---

<section class="bg-black text-white py-6 lg:py-12 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="w-full mx-auto lg:px-12">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center">
      <div class="w-full px-8 lg:w-1/2 mb-12 lg:mb-0 lg:pl-12">
        <p class="text-purple-500 text-xl mb-4 font-medium">04</p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 md:mb-8">
          Blockchain
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 leading-snug">
          From e-invoicing to digital identity, Infinia uses blockchain to ensure transparency, security, and trust in government and enterprise systems.

        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 relative">
        <div class="relative w-full md:rounded-full aspect-square overflow-hidden">
          <Image 
            src={BlockChain} 
            alt="BlockChain" 
            class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-contain" 
            loading="eager" 
            decoding="async"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>